    "is-referenced-by-count": 28,
    "title": [
      "Genome-wide analysis in 756,646 individuals provides first genetic evidence that\n                  <i>ACE2</i>\n                  expression influences COVID-19 risk and yields genetic risk scores predictive of severe disease"
    ],
